>咁你邊到搵把一文字呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淘寶80蚊把，一齊入貨未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶果啲垃圾黎 要買去日本買武士刀</blockquote><br />\n機場一定封鎖左</blockquote><br />\n睇我post 我買左兩把係屋企"},{"pid":"bb5c58f3d80dd6a05d9ecb6034b5f9d7a58c30a7","tid":134652,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌 我都有諗過有喪屍上格床會唔會好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會因為踩唔到其他喪屍而只可以伸手<br />\n但如果有1~2隻跌低左 你就gg</blockquote><br />\n無樓梯上唔上到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1-2隻跌低左，最多咪喪屍踩喪屍高0.5米，趕得切kill最高個隻就唔成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就當你殺晒<br />\n但係屋外既屍一聽/聞到你 就會湧入黎<br />\n1把刀2隻手點頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我建議清晒你碌架床下面既喪屍之後，打返個靚丁先，睇下仲有無喪屍聞到我又聚晒係我下面，<br />\n等一段時間之後再出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df97e3c4f418af093d0e62296fcaa8362f32741","tid":134652,"uid":37067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"跑步機"},{"pid":"48a7ade066d068071cd9487937b586035a0684a0","tid":134652,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你邊到搵把一文字呢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VgGZh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VgGZh3.jpg&h=2b7e11fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06a8bfe65fc61a2f90f86724a67c1822a270ef83","tid":134652,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>left 4 dead 果d識爬梯</blockquote><br />\n出埋charger smoker boomer jokey tabk witch 睇樓主點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我假設遇到普通喪屍咋，睇連登喪屍故都要等一段時間先識變種，到時我都閂到個鐵閘之後隱居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe837017e41febb5917aba1338a9e86fd7add1b2","tid":134652,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁想打丁時點算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n射落去俾喪屍食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果苟雲慧變左喪屍<br />\n係下面 你地會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剝咗佢棚牙 拎返上床屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後巨龍受感染，要切J保命</blockquote><br />\n傻仔 帶套啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌屌下成個閪散到成床都係，入面仲有好多屍蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ad0d0e873a3ddeb2f8956c4020bc4b80f5c35a","tid":134652,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑步機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yRmY2X5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRmY2X5.jpg&h=a5fe18d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實證明係唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，除非你封晒側邊而且跑步機個size fit曬個大門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後較到有咁斜得咁斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71f0807634f1d00e3921712c28b40adbbd405f3","tid":134652,"uid":18753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌 我都有諗過有喪屍上格床會唔會好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會因為踩唔到其他喪屍而只可以伸手<br />\n但如果有1~2隻跌低左 你就gg</blockquote><br />\n無樓梯上唔上到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機<br />\n但係唔排除有機率比一部裝滿喪屍既lift上到黎</blockquote><br />\n妳禁定架lift 上來卡死佢"},{"pid":"036c85e5a33d26bb2ab48cc937b7